nodes.text: Level 5 was a level on the planet Coruscant. It was the lowest inhabitable level of the 5127-levelled ecumenopolis, and was deemed by a young Amilyn Holdo to be the lowest accessible level of the Coruscant Underworld, citing common knowledge. This was not true, however, as Holdo's friend, Leia Organa, piloted an airspeeder down to the derelict Level 4 of the undercity.
